data.description: Have you been searching for a lake home? Please take a look at this large home in New Harborgate subdivsion at  Flat Swamp area of High Rock Lake. Recent updates to include flooring, paint, all oak trim has been stained and gives such a dramatic look to the home. Large country kitchen with center island that can easily accommodate 6 people, granite counter tops with tile backsplash. Main level primary bedroom with same beautiful lake view as the great room, primary also features ensuite bathroom with separate tub and shower. When at the lake entertaining is always considered and this home has its own man cave with bar, motorized impact screen, surround sound system. If you like playing golf, all you need to do is add your own golf simulator. This home has many numerous amenities, make your appointment today to see for yourself.  Bring your boat and dock it at the shared pier, or enjoy the amenities New Harborgate to include pool, playground, tennis and more. Propane gas cooktop.
